    <line>no means of extracting it. <del rend="strikethrough">A</del> My suffering were</line>
    <line>augmented also by the oppressive sense <del rend="strikethrough">I had</del></line>
    <line>of <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">the</add> injustice &amp; ingratitude <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">of their infliction</add>
      </mod> My daily <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">prayers</del>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">vows</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line>rose for revenge &#x2013; a deep &amp; deadly revenge</line>
    <line>such as would alone compensate for the</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">horrors of my situation.</del>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">the outrages &amp; the anguish I had endured.</add>
      </mod></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line rend="indent2">After some weeks my wound healed</line>
    <line>and I continued my journey &#x2014; the labours</line>
    <line>I endured were no longer <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">to be</add>
      </mod> alleviated by the</line>
    <line>bright sun or gent<del rend="strikethrough">t</del>le breezes of spring &#x2014;</line>
    <line>all joy was but <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">a</add> mockery to me, <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough"> &amp;</del>
        <anchor xml:id="c57-0062.01"/>
      </mod></line>
    <line>made me feel more painfully that</line>
    <line>I was not made for enjoyment. But</line>
    <line>my <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">journey</del>
        <add place="superlinear">toils</add>
      </mod> now drew near a close &amp; two</line>
    <line>months from this time I reached the</line>
    <line>environs of Geneva.</line>
